 \iint f \,\, dS = \int_{x = 0}^{x = 1} \int_{y = 0}^{y = 1 - x} (x + y) \, \sqrt{3} \,\, dy \,\, dx. 
 \iint f(x,y,z) dS=\int_{0}^{1}\int_{0}^{1-x} (x+y) \sqrt{1+(\frac{dz}{dx})^{2}+(\frac{dz}{dy})^2}dy\,dx
